{"tid":2128007,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"亞洲城市咁樣衰 其實係咩原因造成？","createTime":"2020-07-27T15:54:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-28T00:52:01.000Z","uid":331739,"like":4,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"d32306a2c465b3f1afd27cb77a877c0198f5f4c0","tid":2128007,"uid":331739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T15:54:36.000Z","msg":"首先比大家睇下圖 呢啲圖我都係喺google map cap街景cap返嚟<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8GHFbuQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8GHFbuQ.png&h=8e6ac29a&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZUrR2Bv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZUrR2Bv.png&h=d744b3bf&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LVjDHBw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLVjDHBw.png&h=956828ee&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Eek0buR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEek0buR.png&h=f76a6961&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/biOAKPR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbiOAKPR.jpg&h=e75188de&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rEYEr3c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrEYEr3c.png&h=3e29324c&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NHr6RuS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNHr6RuS.png&h=915de68f&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TAQO4PT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTAQO4PT.png&h=56d7d52c&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n就咁睇 已經好分別到邊啲係歐洲城市 邊啲係亞洲城市<br />\n亞洲城市一比 真係好柒 頂多可以話係柒得嚟各有特色<br />\n同樣係現代大城市 美學上真係差九皮<br />\n究竟係咩原因做成呢個差距？我諗到有幾個<br />\n<br />\n1. 亞洲玩唔到現代古典主義建築<br />\n亞洲文明自古以來都唔起高樓作為日常用途，高樓例如塔,宮殿,寺廟,都係用喺上層階級嘅人用, 一般建築多數係平房。結果導致現代化時無古典建築參考，只可以起毫無特色嘅現代主義風格樓<br />\n2. 太急於現代化<br />\n亞洲主要城市都係戰後先開始發展，之前除咗日本基本上都係農業社會，大力建設嘅年代已經係現代主義建築流行嘅年代，直接導致而家嘅城市面貌<br />\n3. 亞洲人講實用<br />\n亞洲人鐘意炒樓,起樓最緊要越大越好, 可以賣多百幾呎，要美感嘅話就會犧牲空間<br />\n<br />\n我估係呢啲原因，但係唔知啱唔啱/係咪主要原因，或者有無研究建築嘅巴絲講吓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e531b3fae89e01e3c7e09bb8aa4240e2ff6e493c","tid":2128007,"uid":362900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T15:55:16.000Z","msg":"污染<br />\n<br />\n水，光，氣"},{"pid":"880d0770f8d3d7a970483522a1a3493580f4c0d8","tid":2128007,"uid":344625,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T15:57:07.000Z","msg":"地少人多"},{"pid":"4e440e415976f153ff4373f286e740c8474b7469","tid":2128007,"uid":328232,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T15:59:20.000Z","msg":"urban planning 開始得遲過人、保育有錢有心情先做。當然經濟無人咁強，依d 野就一定唔係個政府首要考慮"},{"pid":"036956a3fc00fedaab92470a1f8dcdfef0d36a62","tid":2128007,"uid":331739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"880d0770f8d3d7a970483522a1a3493580f4c0d8","tid":2128007,"uid":344625,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T15:57:07.000Z","msg":"地少人多"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T16:02:37.000Z","msg":"呢個又衍生另一個問題 點解亞洲人口咁集中喺城市<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04bb281fce59d6e9bf845b40818480d5b817409c","tid":2128007,"uid":334765,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T16:08:06.000Z","msg":"你見啲歐洲大型建築群都係好耐以前起好,佢地傾向保留所以keep到而家<br />\n咁亞洲以前係落後過佢哋,當時冇咩標誌性建築,而後期開始發展所以起啲樓係新得多,又可以話現代建築同以前啲style完全唔同<br />\n新舊程度我覺得係氣候問題,歐洲乾燥好多唔似亞洲咁濕所以佢地啲建築擺好耐都冇大問題,香港嗰啲30-40年打後都已經危樓咁款<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />歐洲嗰啲大把過百年<br />\n樣衰嗰啲例如香港啲唐樓係保養問題,幢樓keep住幾年油一次都可以靚嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d6bfe9476ff44fefd7ee102659a4c7082219f0f","tid":2128007,"uid":331739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"04bb281fce59d6e9bf845b40818480d5b817409c","tid":2128007,"uid":334765,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T16:08:06.000Z","msg":"你見啲歐洲大型建築